Commissioner for Lands and Housing in Sokoto State, Sirajo Marafa Gatawa, is dead. This was disclosed by a family source, who said the late commissioner died at an undisclosed hospital in Sokoto after a protracted illness. Confirming his death, his niece in a social media post said, “Another painful lost this evening, my uncle, Hon. Marafa Gatawa is dead. “May Allah have mercy on him and forgive his sins.” 